# S06-T08: Update Strategy

## Objective
Detect new app versions (SW update) and prompt user to reload at safe moments.

## Acceptance Criteria
- Build embeds version (commit SHA + semver).
- SW `updatefound` event surfaces `useAppUpdate()`.
- Top-bar non-intrusive indicator: "UPDATE AVAILABLE — RELOAD".
- Auto-reload only when user idle ≥ 60s AND not in COMBAT preset.

## Steps
1. Embed version into build via Vite define.
2. Hook SW `updatefound` and `controllerchange`.
3. Build indicator widget.
4. Implement idle + preset gating for auto-reload.

## Invariants
- Never auto-reload during active stream + recording.
- Reload always preserves layout state (localStorage).
- Version visible in debug panel.
